Package com.atakmap.android.resection

Interface ResectionWorkflow

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ResectionDropDownReceiver
    public interface ResectionWorkflow
    Describes a resectioning workflow. This workflow may also be used for describing a GPS-denied navigation aid.

      • getRequiredData

        java.lang.String getRequiredData()
        Gets a description of any datasets required by the tool. For example, a tool may require that DTED data be installed on the device.
        Returns:
        Description of any required data that must be installed. Null or empty string if no data is required.

      • getRequiredHardware
